---
---
<section id="impacto" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white relative border-y border-slate-200">
  <!-- Minimalist Abstract Art Background -->
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full md:w-1/2 opacity-[0.03] md:opacity-5 pointer-events-none z-0">
    <img src="/images/mangrove_abstract.png" alt="" class="object-cover h-full w-full object-right mix-blend-multiply" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-outfit text-[44px] md:text-[56px] text-slate-900 font-light tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.1] mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        El Impacto en Números
      </h2>
      <p class="font-inter text-[15px] font-light text-slate-600 leading-[1.7] max-w-xl">
        La reactivación de La Palma no es solo una visión arquitectónica; es un motor de cambio cuantificable para la economía local y la preservación ecológica.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 md:gap-8">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col border-l border-[#FF6600] pl-6 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="font-outfit text-[56px] md:text-[72px] text-slate-900 font-light tracking-tighter leading-none mb-2">120+</span>
        <span class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-500 uppercase">Familias Beneficiadas</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col border-l border-slate-200 pl-6 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <span class="font-outfit text-[56px] md:text-[72px] text-slate-900 font-light tracking-tighter leading-none mb-2">2.5K</span>
        <span class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-500 uppercase">Hectáreas Protegidas</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col border-l border-slate-200 pl-6 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <span class="font-outfit text-[56px] md:text-[72px] text-slate-900 font-light tracking-tighter leading-none mb-2">50+</span>
        <span class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-500 uppercase">Especies de Aves</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col border-l border-slate-200 pl-6 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
        <span class="font-outfit text-[56px] md:text-[72px] text-[#FF6600] font-light tracking-tighter leading-none mb-2">$0</span>
        <span class="font-inter text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-slate-500 uppercase">Inversión Estatal Actual</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
